dct_title_s: A Map of some of the south and east bounds of Pennsylvania in America, being partly inhabited
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially; depths shown by soundings. Facsim. "From the original in the John Carter Brown Library, 1943." Includes text. From note accompanying map: conceived and issued by William Penn. In portfolio, as issued.
dct_publisher_sm: Providence, R.I. : John Carter Brown Library, 1943 (S.l. : Meriden Gravure Co.)
